Old necromancer
You must meet an old necromancer by the name of Kholai and talk to him; he can help you solve the mystery of the "vanishing" Joon. But Kholai is presently in disgrace and lives in a tower outside the village. Guards are present!
#subobj  1
Find the tower
Kholai's tower is located in the north east of the desert and is guarded by patrols who have orders to prevent all communication between the old Necromancer and anyone else without the Guild's prior approval.
